divs: Sighting DetailsAs i was driving just west of tilden ne,about a mile i saw on the north side of the highway over a farm,i saw a slight V shape row of white lights hovering over this farm,at the time it was raining .I could not pull my car over so i only saw it about 30 seconds,.At first i thought it to be a flock of geese ,but it was white lights and moved slightly and then remained stillover the farm.It was very awe inspiring to see this strange site,i did not feel at all frightened from the site.
Summary: A row of white lights slight V shape
